messages.content: Are you ready for the next battle ?
Indeed, I am ready to face the challenges of the days and nights to come.
No I was just kidding....that's not a battle ...I will just ask you a few questions and I will determine which replies are the best
Sure, I will answer to the best of my ability. What do you want to know?
First question: What is walking on 4 legs in the morning, on 2 legs in the afternoon and on 3 legs at night ?
I will give you a clue...it's not a dog
It is not a dog. It is a cat.
